  "title": "Unique Velvety Egyptian Oats Tagine",
  "description": "A rich and indulgent Egyptian dish featuring rolled oats, cooked to perfection in a clay pot, high in protein and perfect for a special occasion. This unique tagine is a fatty and velvety delight.",
