  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the lamb shoulder and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and cook until the onion is translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the rolled oats, chicken broth, dried apricots, almonds, ras el hanout, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove the clay pot from the heat and let it cool slightly.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional sliced almonds if desired."
